  "response": "My dream house would be a harmonious blend of comfort, functionality, and nature. It would have large windows to let in natural light and offer stunning views of the surrounding landscape. The interior would be open and airy, with a cozy living area, a well-equipped kitchen, and a library filled with books.\n\nThe design would incorporate eco-friendly materials and smart home technology for energy efficiency. Outdoor spaces would feature a garden, perhaps with a small pond or a patio for relaxation and entertaining. Overall, the house would be a peaceful retreat where creativity and relaxation can thrive. How about you? What does your dream house look like?",
